title: Target of Desire: Episode 1
creator: Osgoode Media
description: What happens when a video game character is self-aware? Maia is a video game character, who is followed by men in suits, everywhere she goes, and she doesn't know why. She fights for survival while trying to solve her mystery and understand her reality. Maria is a cryptic character. The only thing that she reveals about herself is that she "works at the University." She blogs (and is on social media) under the username of "IamNamedMaria", where she speculates about the nature of reality.
subject: mystery, science fiction
